trans-unit.source: Manages printers and print jobs.
trans-unit.target: Administrerer skrivere og i køen.

trans-unit.source: Some properties of the PrintQueue object represent characteristics of the print queue utility that runs on the computer, but others represent features or states of the printer itself.
trans-unit.target: Noen egenskaper på objektet utskriftskøen representerer egenskapene for køen verktøyet som kjører på datamaskinen, men andre representerer funksjoner eller tilstander for selve skriveren.

trans-unit.source: For example, <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.NumberOfJobs%2A> is a characteristic of the print queue, but <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location%2A> is a property of the printer.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.NumberOfJobs%2A>er en egenskap for køen, men <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location%2A>er en egenskap for skriveren.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.NumberOfJobs%2A>

trans-unit.source: Many of the properties of the printer, such as whether it needs user attention, need to be passed, by means of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Refresh%2A> method, from the printer itself to the PrintQueue object.
trans-unit.target: Mange av egenskapene for skriveren, for eksempel om den trenger bruker tilsyn må sendes av metoder den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Refresh%2A>metoden fra selve skriveren til utskriftskøen-objekt.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Refresh%2A>

trans-unit.source: This should be done before the corresponding property (<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.NeedUserIntervention%2A>) is read by your program.
trans-unit.target: Dette må gjøres før den tilsvarende egenskapen (<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.NeedUserIntervention%2A>) leses av programmet ditt.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.NeedUserIntervention%2A>

trans-unit.source: Similarly, when your program changes the values of one or more properties of a PrintQueue object, the change must be written to the actual print queue utility on the computer.
trans-unit.target: På samme måte når programmet endres verdiene i én eller flere egenskaper for et objekt for utskriftskøen, må endringen skrives til faktiske køen-verktøyet på datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: Do this with the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Commit%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Gjør dette det <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Commit%2A>metode.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Commit%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Klasser i den <xref:System.Printing>navneområdet støttes ikke for bruk i en Windows ASP.NET-program eller tjeneste.</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Attempting to use these classes from within one of these application types may produce unexpected problems, such as diminished service performance and run-time exceptions.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å bruke disse klassene fra i ett av disse programtyper kan føre til uventede problemer, for eksempel dårligere tjeneste ytelse og kjøretid unntak.

trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil skrive ut fra en Windows Forms-program, kan du se den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>navneområde.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Use this method to write device specific information, to a spool file, that is not automatically included by the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] spooler.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å skrive bestemte enhetsinformasjon, til en spool-fil som ikke er inkludert i automatisk av [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] køen.

trans-unit.source: Of course, you need to know whether the spool file is [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_emf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-emf-md.md)] or [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This array is what prints if the printer is working and is not paused.
trans-unit.target: Denne matrisen er hva skriver hvis skriveren fungerer og er ikke stanset midlertidig.

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > If the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.JobStream%2A> is not closed with <xref:System.IO.Stream.Close%2A> before the end of the thread in which AddJob is called, then an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> is thrown when that thread ends because the spooler thread cannot gain control over the <xref:System.IO.Stream> object.

trans-unit.source: The call to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_com](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-com-md.md)] requires that the calling thread have a single-threaded apartment (<xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>) instead of multiple-threaded apartment (<xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>) which is the default in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_net](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-net-md.md)] 2.0 and later.
trans-unit.target: Kallet til [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_com](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-com-md.md)] krever at kall tråden har en single-threaded apartment (<xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>) i stedet for flere-threaded apartment (<xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>) som er standard i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_net](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-net-md.md)] 2.0 og senere.</xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState> </xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>

trans-unit.source: (For more on threading and apartment states, see [Managed and Unmanaged Threading](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/db425c20-4b2f-4433-bf96-76071c7881e5), and <xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>.) There are two ways of doing this: - The simplest way is to add the <xref:System.STAThreadAttribute> (that is, "`[System.STAThreadAttribute()]`") just above the first line of the application's `Main` method (usually "`static void Main(string[] args)`").
trans-unit.target: (For mer informasjon om threading og apartment tilstand, kan du se [behandlede og uforvaltede Threading](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/db425c20-4b2f-4433-bf96-76071c7881e5), og <xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>.)</xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState> Det er to måter å gjøre dette:-er den enkleste måten å legge til den <xref:System.STAThreadAttribute>(det vil si "`[System.STAThreadAttribute()]`") like over den første linjen i programmets `Main` metoden (vanligvis "`static void Main(string[] args)`").</xref:System.STAThreadAttribute>

trans-unit.source: - If you need your `Main` thread's apartment state to be <xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>, you can house the call to AddJob in a separate thread whose apartment state is set to <xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState> with <xref:System.Threading.Thread.SetApartmentState%2A>.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis du trenger din `Main` trådens apartment tilstand for å være <xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>, du kan inneholde kallet til AddJob i en separat tråd der apartment-statusen er satt til <xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>med <xref:System.Threading.Thread.SetApartmentState%2A>.</xref:System.Threading.Thread.SetApartmentState%2A> </xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState> </xref:System.Threading.ApartmentState>

trans-unit.source: The example below illustrates this second technique.
trans-unit.target: Eksemplet nedenfor viser den andre metoden.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > You cannot apply the <xref:System.STAThreadAttribute> to any method except `Main` and you cannot use <xref:System.Threading.Thread.SetApartmentState%2A> for the `Main` thread.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Kan du bruke den <xref:System.STAThreadAttribute>til en metode unntatt `Main` ikke <xref:System.Threading.Thread.SetApartmentState%2A>for den `Main` tråd.</xref:System.Threading.Thread.SetApartmentState%2A> </xref:System.STAThreadAttribute>

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobSettings"> </xref> verdi som inneholder innstillingene for øyeblikket jobben.

trans-unit.source: These settings include a description of the job and a reference to the job's <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Disse innstillingene inkluderer en beskrivelse av jobben og en referanse til prosjektets <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the default printer options associated with this <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir til standardalternativene som er tilknyttet denne <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> specifies print job options such as <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.CopyCount%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageOrientation%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Duplexing%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Stapling%2A>, and others.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>angir utskriftsjobben alternativer som <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.CopyCount%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageOrientation%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Duplexing%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Stapling%2A>, og andre.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Stapling%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.Duplexing%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageOrientation%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.CopyCount%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> maintains its own DefaultPrintTicket.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>opprettholder sin egen DefaultPrintTicket.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: In normal operation the DefaultPrintTicket property returns a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen returnerer normal drift av DefaultPrintTicket <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> detects an invalid state, DefaultPrintTicket returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>oppdager en ugyldig tilstand DefaultPrintTicket returnerer `null`.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: If DefaultPrintTicket returns `null`, the application should display an informational user dialog that an error has occurred on this print queue and that the print job should be restarted with the output directed to a different print queue.
trans-unit.target: Hvis DefaultPrintTicket returnerer `null`, programmet skal vise en brukerdialogboks som informasjon som har oppstått en feil på denne trykt køen, og at utskriftsjobben må startes på nytt med utdata rettet mot en annen trykt kø.

trans-unit.source: Getting or setting the DefaultPrintTicket property does not validate the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir DefaultPrintTicket-egenskapen kan ikke valideres <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A> method can be used to validate a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>Metoden kan brukes til å validere <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>

trans-unit.source: The default <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> for the print queue; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if an error has occurred in the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> for køen; eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis det oppstod en feil i køen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the default priority that is given to each new print job added to the queue.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir standardprioriteten som er angitt til hver ny utskriftsjobben lagt til i køen.

trans-unit.source: A print job's priority can be changed by users after it enters the print queue.
trans-unit.target: En utskriftsjobben prioritet kan endres av brukere når den går inn i køen.

trans-unit.source: The default priority for print jobs added to the queue.
trans-unit.target: Standardprioritet jobbene lagt til i køen.

trans-unit.source: Possible values range from 1 through 99.
trans-unit.target: Mulige verdier er mellom 1 og 99.

trans-unit.source: The default is 1.
trans-unit.target: Standard er 1.

trans-unit.source: Gets a description of the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Henter en beskrivelse for køen.

trans-unit.source: When the queue is created, the description defaults to a three part string that consists of the queue name, model, and location separated by commas.
trans-unit.target: Når køen er opprettet, beskrivelsen som standard til en tre deler streng som består av kønavn, modellen, og plassering atskilt med semikolon.

trans-unit.source: Contrast the Description property with the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment%2A> property which is visible to users in the common print dialog and the Printers and Faxes list.
trans-unit.target: Kontrast Description-egenskapen med den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment%2A>som er synlige for brukerne i vanlige utskriftsdialogboksen og skrivere og telefakser.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment%2A>

trans-unit.source: A description of the print queue.
trans-unit.target: En beskrivelse for køen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the complete name of the queue.
trans-unit.target: Henter fullstendig navn for køen.

trans-unit.source: For print queues on the local print server, this property's value is identical to <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Name%2A>, otherwise it includes the full UNC (Universal Naming Convention) name.
trans-unit.target: Skriv ut køer på lokale serveren, verdien for denne egenskapen er identisk med <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Name%2A>, hvis den inneholder hele navnet i UNC-(Universal Naming Convention).</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object also has writeable <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Name%2A> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objektet har også skrivbare <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Name%2A>og <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Name%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: The complete name of the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Det fullstendige navnet på køen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintCapabilities"></xref> object that identifies the capabilities of the printer.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintCapabilities"> </xref> -objekt som identifiserer funksjoner for skriveren.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintCapabilities"></xref> object that specifies what the printer can and cannot do, such as two-sided coping or automatic stapling.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Printing.PrintCapabilities"> </xref> objekt som angir hva skriveren kan og ikke kan gjøre, for eksempel begge sider skriveforsøk eller automatisk stifting.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintCapabilities"></xref> object that identifies the capabilities of the printer.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Printing.PrintCapabilities"> </xref> -objekt som identifiserer funksjoner for skriveren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> parameter is used as the basis on which to construct the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>parameteren brukes som grunnlag for konstruere den <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>objektet.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: For example, suppose the printer supported only media types A and B from input bin 1 and it only supported media type C from input bin 2.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel anta skriveren støttes bare media typer A og B fra inndataene posisjon 1 og den støttes bare medietypen C fra inndataene posisjon 2.

trans-unit.source: If the `printTicket` parameter specified input bin 1, then the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> object that is returned would include all three media types, but it would report type C as "constrained."
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `printTicket` parameter angitt inndata posisjon 1, og deretter i <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>objektet som returneres omfatter alle tre media typer, men det ble rapportert C-type som "begrenset."</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>

trans-unit.source: If the `printTicket` parameter specified input bin 2, then the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> object that is returned would include all three media types, but it would report types A and B as "constrained."
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `printTicket` parameter angitt inndata posisjon 2, og deretter på <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>objektet som returneres omfatter alle tre media typer, men det ble rapportert typer A og B som "begrenset."</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> parameter is used as the basis on which to construct the print capabilities XML.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>parameteren brukes som grunnlag for konstruere utskriftsfunksjonen XML.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: For example, suppose the printer supported only media types A and B from input bin 1 and it only supported media type C from input bin 2.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel anta skriveren støttes bare media typer A og B fra inndataene posisjon 1 og den støttes bare medietypen C fra inndataene posisjon 2.

trans-unit.source: If the `printTicket` parameter specified input bin 1, then the print capabilities XML that is returned would include all three media types, but it would report type C as "constrained."
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `printTicket` parameter angitt inndata posisjon 1, og deretter utskriftsfunksjonen XML som returneres omfatter alle tre media typer, men det ble rapportert C-type som "begrenset."

trans-unit.source: If the `printTicket` parameter specified input bin 2, then the print capabilities XML that is returned would include all three media types, but it would report types A and B as "constrained."
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `printTicket` parameter angitt inndata posisjon 2, og deretter utskriftsfunksjonen XML som returneres omfatter alle tre media typer, men det ble rapportert typer A og B som "begrenset."

trans-unit.source: See the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397) for more information on constraints.
trans-unit.target: Se den [Skriv ut skjemaet](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397) for mer informasjon om begrensninger.

trans-unit.source: If `printTicket` is `null`, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UserPrintTicket%2A> is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `printTicket` er `null`, <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UserPrintTicket%2A>brukes.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UserPrintTicket%2A>

trans-unit.source: The two tickets are then merged.

trans-unit.source: The name of the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på køen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the printer needs the attention of a human being.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om skriveren må handling for en person.

trans-unit.source: If the printer does not support a signal with this meaning, then the property is always `false`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis skriveren støtter ikke et signal med denne betydning, og deretter egenskapen er alltid `false`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the printer needs human attention; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis skriveren må Personal Obs; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the total number of jobs lined up in the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Henter det totale antallet jobber som er ordnet i køen.

trans-unit.source: The number of jobs in the queue.
trans-unit.target: Antall jobber i køen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the printer is unable to print the current page.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om skriveren ikke kan skrive ut gjeldende side.

trans-unit.source: If the printer does not support a signal with this meaning, then the property is always `false`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis skriveren støtter ikke et signal med denne betydning, og deretter egenskapen er alltid `false`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the printer is unable to print the current page; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis de ikke kan skrive ut den gjeldende siden. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Pauses the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Stopper midlertidig køen.

trans-unit.source: It remains paused until <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Resume*> is executed.
trans-unit.target: Det er midlertidig stanset før <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Resume*>er utført.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Resume*>

trans-unit.source: The printer cannot be paused.
trans-unit.target: Kan ikke stanses midlertidig skriveren.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the current print job is being cancelled.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om den gjeldende utskriftsjobben blir avbrutt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the print job is being cancelled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis utskriftsjobben blir avbrutt; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the priority of the print queue relative to other print queues that are hosted by the same print server and that use the same physical printer.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir prioriteten for køen i forhold til andre trykt køer som er vert samme serveren, og som bruker den samme fysiske skriveren.

trans-unit.source: Contrast this property with the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.DefaultPriority%2A> property which is about the relative priority of print jobs in the queue.
trans-unit.target: Kontrast egenskapen med den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.DefaultPriority%2A>som er om relative prioriteten for jobbene i køen.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.DefaultPriority%2A>

trans-unit.source: The priority for the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Prioriteten for køen.

trans-unit.source: Possible values are from 1 through 99.
trans-unit.target: Mulige verdier er mellom 1 og 99.

trans-unit.source: The default is 1.
trans-unit.target: Standard er 1.

trans-unit.source: Removes all the jobs in the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner alle jobber i køen.

trans-unit.source: Some print jobs could not be removed from the queue.
trans-unit.target: Noen jobbene kan ikke fjernes fra køen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the properties of the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Henter egenskapene for køen.

trans-unit.source: A bitwise combination of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueAttributes"></xref> enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: En bitvis kombinasjon av det <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueAttributes"> </xref> nummereringsverdier.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the printer driver for the queue.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir driveren for køen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Printing.PrintDriver"></xref> that the queue uses.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintDriver"> </xref> som bruker køen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the port that the queue uses.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir porten som bruker køen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Printing.PrintPort"></xref> that is assigned to the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintPort"> </xref> som er tilordnet til køen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the print processor that the queue uses.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir trykt prosessoren køen bruker.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Printing.PrintProcessor"></xref> that the queue uses, such as WinPrint or ModiPrint.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintProcessor"> </xref> som køen bruker, for eksempel WinPrint eller ModiPrint.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that represents the status of the printer.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som representerer statusen for skriveren.

trans-unit.source: These include "warming up," "initializing," "printing," and others.
trans-unit.target: Disse omfatter "Varmer," "initialisering", "utskrift" og andre.

trans-unit.source: The current <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueStatus"></xref> value.
trans-unit.target: Gjeldende <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueStatus"> </xref> verdi.

trans-unit.source: Updates the properties of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"></xref> object with values from the printer and the print queue utility that runs on the computer.
trans-unit.target: Oppdaterer egenskapene for den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueue"> </xref> objektet med verdiene fra skriveren og køen verktøyet som kjører på datamaskinen.

trans-unit.source: Changes your program makes to a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object's properties are lost when Refresh executes, unless they have been written to the printer and print queue with <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Commit%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Endringene dine blir til en <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objektegenskapene går tapt når oppdatering utfører, med mindre de er skrevet til skriveren og skrive ut køen med <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Commit%2A>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Commit%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: Some of the properties could not be refreshed.
trans-unit.target: Enkelte egenskaper kan ikke oppdateres.

trans-unit.source: Restarts a print queue that was paused.
trans-unit.target: Starter en print kø ble stoppet midlertidig.

trans-unit.source: The printer cannot resume.
trans-unit.target: Skriveren kan ikke fortsette.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the printer prints jobs that have completed the spooling process before jobs that have not fully spooled even if the latter entered the queue first or have a higher priority.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om skrives jobber som har fullført ventende prosessen før jobber som ikke er fullstendig i kø selv om den siste angitte køen første eller høyere prioritet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the printer prints jobs that have completed the spooling process before jobs that have not fully spooled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis skrives jobber som har fullført ventende prosessen før jobber som ikke er fullstendig i kø; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the path and file name of a file that is inserted at the beginning of each print job.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir banen og filnavnet til en fil som er satt inn i begynnelsen av hver utskriftsjobben.

trans-unit.source: This is normally a single-page file used to make it easier to separate the output of different print jobs.
trans-unit.target: Dette er vanligvis en én-fil som brukes til å gjøre det enklere å skille resultatet av forskjellige i køen.

trans-unit.source: The path and file name of the separator file.
trans-unit.target: Banen og navnet på filen skilletegn.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a name for the printer that is seen by users on the network when it is shared.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et navn for skriveren er synlig for brukere på nettverket, når den er delt.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object also has a read only <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.FullName%2A> property and a writeable <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Name%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objektet også er en skrivebeskyttet <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.FullName%2A>egenskapen og en skrivbar <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Name%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Name%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.FullName%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: For queues on the local print server, these properties have the same value.
trans-unit.target: Disse egenskapene har samme verdi for køer på lokale serveren.

trans-unit.source: The public name of a shared printer.
trans-unit.target: Fellesnavn på en delt skriver.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the earliest time of day, expressed as the number of minutes after midnight Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) (also called Greenwich Mean Time [GMT]), that the printer will print a job.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir det tidligste tidspunktet på dagen, uttrykt som antall minutter etter midnatt Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) (også kalt Greenwich mellomtiden [GMT]), at skriveren skriver ut en jobb.

trans-unit.source: The time of day that the printer first becomes available, expressed as the number of minutes after midnight (UTC).
trans-unit.target: Klokkeslettet som skriveren først er tilgjengelig, uttrykt som antall minutter etter midnatt (UTC).

trans-unit.source: The maximum value is 1439.
trans-unit.target: Maksimumsverdien er 1439.

trans-unit.source: When a printer is first installed by using the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Add Printer Wizard, the printer defaults to being available all the time, and this property returns 0 in all time zones.
trans-unit.target: Når en skriver først installeres ved hjelp av [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] veiviseren skriveren bruker til å bli tilgjengelig hele tiden, og denne egenskapen returnerer 0 i alle tidssoner.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the latest time, expressed as the number of minutes after midnight Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) (also called Greenwich Mean Time [GMT]), that the printer will print a job.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir det siste tidspunktet uttrykt som antall minutter etter midnatt Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) (også kalt Greenwich mellomtiden [GMT]), at skriveren skriver ut en jobb.

trans-unit.source: The time of day that the printer is no longer available, expressed as the number of minutes after midnight (UTC).
trans-unit.target: Klokkeslettet som ikke lenger tilgjengelig, uttrykt som antall minutter etter midnatt (UTC).

trans-unit.source: The maximum value is 1439.
trans-unit.target: Maksimumsverdien er 1439.

trans-unit.source: When a printer is first installed by using the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Add Printer Wizard, the printer defaults to being available all the time, and this property returns 0 in all time zones.
trans-unit.target: Når en skriver først installeres ved hjelp av [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] veiviseren skriveren bruker til å bli tilgjengelig hele tiden, og denne egenskapen returnerer 0 i alle tidssoner.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the current user's default <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> object which contains detailed information about the print job.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den gjeldende brukeren standard <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> objektet som inneholder detaljert informasjon om utskriftsjobben.

trans-unit.source: Each user can have his or her own default <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.
trans-unit.target: Hver enkelt bruker kan ha sin egen standard <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: This property can be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan være `null`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> for the current user, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if a user <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> has not been specified.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> for den gjeldende brukeren eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis en bruker <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> er ikke angitt.
